Hello <%= @user.username.presence || @user.name.presence || 'player' %>,

Your Maddox Gaming order #<%= @order.id %> is now <%= @order.status %>.

Amount: <%= @order.currency %> <%= format('%.2f', @order.total_amount.to_f) %>
Payment method: <%= @order.payment_method %>
Gateway: <%= @order.gateway_name %>
Reference: <%= @order.payment_reference %>
Transaction ID: <%= @order.transaction_id.presence || 'Pending confirmation' %>

<% if @order.paid? %>
Thank you for your purchase.
<% else %>
Your payment did not complete successfully. Return to checkout to retry.
<% end %>
